rows.label: qst103316_msg0001
rows.name:
Amazing! There was no need
for me to do anything!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0004
rows.name:
I only told them the lady's schedule.
I never thought she'd be killed!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0005
rows.name: That's right, these guys... I think...

rows.label: qst103316_msg0006
rows.name: Here's the key to their hideout!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0007
rows.name:
They gather in an old warehouse
in the lower level of the city.

rows.label: qst103316_msg0008
rows.name: Yes, that's right! It's not a lie!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0009
rows.name:
I'm providing information
that's disadvantageous to
them! I'm not one of them!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0122
rows.name:
Even if you're not one of
them, I'm going to make you
tell me everything you know!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0151
rows.name:
I didn't know they were going to
kill the lady! It's the truth!!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0152
rows.name:
We'll hear the rest of your
story at military headquarters!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0181
rows.name:
I will take this man
into custody myself!

rows.label: qst103316_msg0182
rows.name:
Could I ask you to
investigate the hideout?

rows.label: qst103316_msg0183
rows.name:
After I hand this man over to the
military, I will head there as well!
